    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented justification. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. The assessment supports pre-market submission for the Class II CPB device within the operating envelope described in the claim and requirement documentation.",
